room_title: Escape room "Mysterious Stranger" by Steal and Escape in San Diego
room_address: 2602 Transportation Avenue, Suite B, National City, CA 91950
room_description: You've just received a really unusual phone call. The CIA need your help in a bomb threat case. Your neighbor has been developing a device that could possibly destroy half of America. During interrogation, he found a way to activate it, and the operatives will not be able to reach it in time. You have an hour to sneak in and locate the device.
